    <lb n="4a"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"> χρη</supplied>ματισθέντος δὲ αὐτοῖς καὶ εἰς ἕκαστον σφῆνα παρ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> 

